OL,3,CAlmost 600,000 council jobs lost in a
OL,4,Cdecade ` union
OL,6,FCouncils across England and Wales have
OL,7,Flost almost a third of their staff
OL,8,Fover the past decade, according to new
OL,9,Fresearch.
OL,11,FA study by the GMB revealed that since
OL,12,F2012, almost 600,000 council jobs had
OL,13,Fgone.
OL,15,FThe union said that 13 years ago,
OL,16,Flocal authorities in England and Wales
OL,17,Femployed 1,894,700 workers, but by
OL,18,F2024 the number had fallen to
OL,19,F1,295,300.
