OL,3,CAlmost 600,000 council jobs lost in a
OL,4,Cdecade ` union
OL,6,FBirmingham was the worst hit council,
OL,7,Flosing almost 27,000 workers, followed
OL,8,Fby Derbyshire and Staffordshire,
OL,9,Faccording to the study.
OL,11,FThe figures were released as the GMB
OL,12,Fand other unions begin talks with the
OL,13,FLocal Government Association over
OL,14,Fcouncil workers' pay claim for 2025/26.
OL,16,FKevin Brandstatter, GMB national
OL,17,Fofficer, said: "These figures are
OL,18,Fclearly appalling and show the deep
OL,19,Fand lasting damage austerity has done
OL,20,Fto our country.
